"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" has told you. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 31:3","book":"Deu","chapter":31,"verse":3},{"label":"Jos 3:11","book":"Jos","chapter":3,"verse":11},{"label":"Ex 24:17","book":"Exo","chapter":24,"verse":17},{"label":"Dt 4:24","book":"Deu","chapter":4,"verse":24},{"label":"Is 29:6","book":"Isa","chapter":29,"verse":6},{"label":"Is 30:27","book":"Isa","chapter":30,"verse":27},{"label":"Is 30:30","book":"Isa","chapter":30,"verse":30},{"label":"Is 33:14","book":"Isa","chapter":33,"verse":14},{"label":"Ezk 15:7","book":"Ezk","chapter":15,"verse":7},{"label":"Ezk 19:12","book":"Ezk","chapter":19,"verse":12},{"label":"Dt 12:2","book":"Deu","chapter":12,"verse":2},{"label":"Jos 23:13","book":"Jos","chapter":23,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God drives them out before you, do not say to yourself, ‘The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" brought me in to take possession of this land because of my righteousness.’ "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 31:1","book":"Psa","chapter":31,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 89:16","book":"Psa","chapter":89,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 119:40","book":"Psa","chapter":119,"verse":40,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 14:14","book":"Ezk","chapter":14,"verse":14,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 14:20","book":"Ezk","chapter":14,"verse":20,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 18:22","book":"Ezk","chapter":18,"verse":22,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" Instead, the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" will drive out these nations before you because of their wickedness. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 11:5","book":"Pro","chapter":11,"verse":5,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 31:1","book":"Psa","chapter":31,"verse":1},{"label":"Ps 89:16","book":"Psa","chapter":89,"verse":16},{"label":"Ps 119:40","book":"Psa","chapter":119,"verse":40},{"label":"Ezk 14:14","book":"Ezk","chapter":14,"verse":14},{"label":"Ezk 14:20","book":"Ezk","chapter":14,"verse":20},{"label":"Ezk 18:22","book":"Ezk","chapter":18,"verse":22},{"label":"Pr 11:5","book":"Pro","chapter":11,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You are not going to take possession of their land because of your righteousness or your integrity. Instead, the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God will drive out these nations before you because of their wickedness, in order to fulfill the promise he swore to your ancestors Abraham, Isaac, and Jacob. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Understand that the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God is not giving you this good land "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 8:7","book":"Deu","chapter":8,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" to possess because of your righteousness, for you are a stiff-necked people. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 32:9","book":"Exo","chapter":32,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 33:3","book":"Exo","chapter":33,"verse":3,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 33:5","book":"Exo","chapter":33,"verse":5,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 34:9","book":"Exo","chapter":34,"verse":9,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 9:13","book":"Deu","chapter":9,"verse":13,"letter":"f"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 8:7","book":"Deu","chapter":8,"verse":7},{"label":"Ex 32:9","book":"Exo","chapter":32,"verse":9},{"label":"Ex 33:3","book":"Exo","chapter":33,"verse":3},{"label":"Ex 33:5","book":"Exo","chapter":33,"verse":5},{"label":"Ex 34:9","book":"Exo","chapter":34,"verse":9},{"label":"Dt 9:13","book":"Deu","chapter":9,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Remember Ex 32–34 and do not forget how you provoked the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God in the wilderness. You have been rebelling against the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" from the day you left the land of Egypt until you reached this place. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You provoked the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" at Horeb, and he was angry enough with you to destroy you. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When I went up the mountain to receive the stone tablets, the tablets of the covenant "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 24:12","book":"Exo","chapter":24,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 31:18","book":"Exo","chapter":31,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 9:11","book":"Deu","chapter":9,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 9:15","book":"Deu","chapter":9,"verse":15,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 9:4","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":4,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" made with you, I stayed on the mountain forty days and forty nights. I did not eat food or drink water. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 24:12","book":"Exo","chapter":24,"verse":12},{"label":"Ex 31:18","book":"Exo","chapter":31,"verse":18},{"label":"Dt 9:11","book":"Deu","chapter":9,"verse":11},{"label":"Dt 9:15","book":"Deu","chapter":9,"verse":15},{"label":"Heb 9:4","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On the day of the assembly the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" gave me the two stone tablets, inscribed by God’s finger. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 8:19","book":"Exo","chapter":8,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 31:18","book":"Exo","chapter":31,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 11:20","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:6","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":6,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" The exact words were on them, which the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" spoke to you from the fire on the mountain. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 5:4","book":"Deu","chapter":5,"verse":4,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 5:22","book":"Deu","chapter":5,"verse":22,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 10:4","book":"Deu","chapter":10,"verse":4,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 8:19","book":"Exo","chapter":8,"verse":19},{"label":"Ex 31:18","book":"Exo","chapter":31,"verse":18},{"label":"Lk 11:20","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":20},{"label":"Jn 8:6","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":6},{"label":"Dt 5:4","book":"Deu","chapter":5,"verse":4},{"label":"Dt 5:22","book":"Deu","chapter":5,"verse":22},{"label":"Dt 10:4","book":"Deu","chapter":10,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" gave me the two stone tablets, the tablets of the covenant, at the end of the forty days and forty nights."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" said to me, ‘Get up and go down immediately from here. For your people whom you brought out of Egypt have acted corruptly. They have quickly turned from the way that I commanded them; they have made a cast image for themselves.’ "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 32:4","book":"Exo","chapter":32,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 32:8","book":"Exo","chapter":32,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 34:17","book":"Exo","chapter":34,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 19:4","book":"Lev","chapter":19,"verse":4,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 33:52","book":"Num","chapter":33,"verse":52,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 27:15","book":"Deu","chapter":27,"verse":15,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 32:4","book":"Exo","chapter":32,"verse":4},{"label":"Ex 32:8","book":"Exo","chapter":32,"verse":8},{"label":"Ex 34:17","book":"Exo","chapter":34,"verse":17},{"label":"Lv 19:4","book":"Lev","chapter":19,"verse":4},{"label":"Nm 33:52","book":"Num","chapter":33,"verse":52},{"label":"Dt 27:15","book":"Deu","chapter":27,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" also said to me, ‘I have seen this people, and indeed, they are a stiff-necked people. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Leave me alone, and I will destroy them and blot out their name under heaven. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 17:14","book":"Exo","chapter":17,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 25:19","book":"Deu","chapter":25,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 29:20","book":"Deu","chapter":29,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 32:26","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":26,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 14:27","book":"2Ki","chapter":14,"verse":27,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 51:1","book":"Psa","chapter":51,"verse":1,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 51:9","book":"Psa","chapter":51,"verse":9,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 18:23","book":"Jer","chapter":18,"verse":23,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" Then I will make you into a nation stronger and more numerous than they.’"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 17:14","book":"Exo","chapter":17,"verse":14},{"label":"Dt 25:19","book":"Deu","chapter":25,"verse":19},{"label":"Dt 29:20","book":"Deu","chapter":29,"verse":20},{"label":"Dt 32:26","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":26},{"label":"2Kg 14:27","book":"2Ki","chapter":14,"verse":27},{"label":"Ps 51:1","book":"Psa","chapter":51,"verse":1},{"label":"Ps 51:9","book":"Psa","chapter":51,"verse":9},{"label":"Jr 18:23","book":"Jer","chapter":18,"verse":23}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“So I went back down the mountain, while it was blazing with fire, and the two tablets of the covenant were in my hands. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I saw how you had sinned against the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God; you had made a calf image for yourselves. You had quickly turned from the way the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" had commanded for you. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So I took hold of the two tablets and threw them from my hands, shattering them before your eyes. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 32:19","book":"Exo","chapter":32,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 32:19","book":"Exo","chapter":32,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I fell down like the first time in the presence of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" for forty days and forty nights; I did not eat food or drink water because of all the sin you committed, doing what was evil in the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s sight and angering him. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I was afraid of the fierce anger the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" had directed against you, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 12:21","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" because he was about to destroy you. But again the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" listened to me on that occasion. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 10:10","book":"Deu","chapter":10,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Heb 12:21","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":21},{"label":"Dt 10:10","book":"Deu","chapter":10,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" was angry enough with Aaron to destroy him. But I prayed for Aaron at that time also. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I took the sinful calf you had made and burned it. I crushed it, thoroughly grinding it to powder as fine as dust, and threw its dust into the stream that came down from the mountain. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 32:20","book":"Exo","chapter":32,"verse":20,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 32:20","book":"Exo","chapter":32,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“You continued to provoke the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" at Taberah, Massah, and Kibroth-hattaavah. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 17:1–7","book":"Exo","chapter":17,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 11:1","book":"Num","chapter":11,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 17:1–7","book":"Exo","chapter":17,"verse":1},{"label":"Nm 11:1","book":"Num","chapter":11,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" sent you from Kadesh-barnea, he said, ‘Go up and possess the land I have given you’; you rebelled against the command of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God. You did not believe or obey him. Nm 13–14 "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You have been rebelling against the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" ever since I have "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Sam, LXX read since he has"},{"kind":"text","text":" known you. Ps 95106"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Sam, LXX read since he has"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“I fell down in the presence of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" forty days and forty nights because the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" had threatened to destroy you. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I prayed to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":":"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Remember your servants Abraham, Isaac, and Jacob. Disregard this people’s stubbornness, and their wickedness and sin. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Otherwise, those in the land you brought us from will say, ‘Because the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" wasn’t able to bring them into the land he had promised them, and because he hated them, he brought them out to kill them in the wilderness.’ "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 14:16","book":"Num","chapter":14,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 14:16","book":"Num","chapter":14,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:9:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But they are your people, your inheritance, whom you brought out by your great power and outstretched arm. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 17:36","book":"2Ki","chapter":17,"verse":36,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Neh 1:10","book":"Neh","chapter":1,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 27:5","book":"Jer","chapter":27,"verse":5,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 32:17","book":"Jer","chapter":32,"verse":17,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Kg 17:36","book":"2Ki","chapter":17,"verse":36},{"label":"Neh 1:10","book":"Neh","chapter":1,"verse":10},{"label":"Jr 27:5","book":"Jer","chapter":27,"verse":5},{"label":"Jr 32:17","book":"Jer","chapter":32,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783099261566}